    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There Is No Escape:  (TINE) Is a 2D Puzzle-platformer built in Clickteam Fusion 2.5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WHAT IS THERE IS NO ESCAPE?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no Escape is a storyless 2D side-scrolling puzzle platformer, it was inspired by early to late 2000's flash games of a similar nature. Jump, fail, repeat!  Experience the nostalgia of the classic platforming genre. <br> <br><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Retro Platforming</strong> - Experience the old platforming mechanics that were common with old flash games! Built for Keyboard and even Controllers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements</strong> - Do you like collecting achievements? So do we! This game has plenty to collect for those achievement hunters out there!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Many levels &amp; themes </strong>- There is many levels to play through, with many different variations, such as the main track, caves, and even the behind the scenes areas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectibles </strong>- There are many things to collect! Collect points or destroy CCTV cameras! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level Select</strong> - Want to return to a specific level after beating the game? We have got you covered! Upon completing the game, you will unlock the Level Select menu!</p></li></ul>",
